<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_4aa6ea82a0bf.aspx"><b>夜过借园见主人坐月下吹笛</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e6%b8%85%e4%bb%a3">清代</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e8%a2%81%e6%9e%9a">袁枚</a></p>
