<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_0795b7d63e8d.aspx"><b>州桥</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%ae%8b%e4%bb%a3">宋代</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e8%8c%83%e6%88%90%e5%a4%a7">范成大</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson0795b7d63e8d">
<p><span style="font-family:SimSun;">南望朱雀门，北望宣德楼，皆旧御路也。</span></p>
<p>州桥南北是天街，父老年年等驾回。<br />忍泪失声询使者，&quot;几时真有六军来？&quot; </p>
